. - single character 
* - match any number of previous (including 0)
\+ - match any number of previous (not 0)
$- end of the line 
^- beginning of the line 
\S - any non-whitespace character 
\s - any whitespace character 
? -optional 
[a-z] - any lowercase letter 
[A-Z] - any uppercase letter 
[A-Za-z] - any letter 
[0-9] - any number 

\ -escape something 

#matching some patterns 

#websites
https://facebook.com 
http://wolfandswallow.xyz/ 
http://kakshya.org/donate/

grep "https\?://\S*\.[A-Za-z]\+\S*" websites

#email 

sailesh@gmail.com 

"\S\+@\S\+.[a-zA-Z]\+" 
